headline: Murphy USA Q1 Earnings Fall Short as Fuel Volumes Decline
summary: MUSA's revenues from petroleum product sales came in at $3.5 billion in first-quarter 2025, below our estimate of $3.7 billion and down 8.4% from a year ago.
